title: Euro.Truck.Simulator.2.v1.30.0.12s.Incl.54.Dlcs.Repack
description: In the "Euro Truck Simulator 2" the player is waiting for even more truck models and the vast expanses of Europe. The player will be able to drive behind the wheel of the best trucks, plowing the endless expanses of the roads of Europe. Naturally, at once no one will give such a truck. To get it, the player has a lot to do. Starting his way with an ordinary hard worker, the player has to travel a lot of miles before he accumulates on the first good tractor. If he does not stop there, he will soon be able to open his own business in the field of cargo transportation, and later, perhaps, to become the head of the transport empire
